languages.text: "Всю жизнь на Футфоле провел. Слышал, на планетах то темно, то светло... ерунда какая-то!"
"I've spent my whole life on Footfall. I've heard that on the planets it goes between dark and light... what a nonsense!"

languages.text: «He vivido toda mi vida en Paso. Dicen que, en los planetas, todo va oscureciéndose y volviendo a iluminarse a lo largo del día... ¡vaya tontería!».
languages.original_text: "I've spent my whole life on Footfall. I've heard that on the planets it goes between dark and light... what a nonsense!"

languages.text: 「生まれてから一度もフットフォールを出たことがない。惑星では闇と光の間を行ったり来たりするとか…馬鹿らしい！」
languages.original_text: "I've spent my whole life on Footfall. I've heard that on the planets it goes between dark and light... what a nonsense!"

traits.locale_text: 「生まれてから一度もフットフォールを出たことがない。惑星では闇と光の間を行ったり来たりするとか…馬鹿らしい！」

languages.text: "Ich habe mein ganzes Leben auf Footfall verbracht. Angeblich wechseln sich auf anderen Planeten Licht und Dunkelheit ab ... so ein Unsinn!"
languages.original_text: "I've spent my whole life on Footfall. I've heard that on the planets it goes between dark and light... what a nonsense!"

languages.text: « Je n'ai jamais rien connu d'autre que Castel. Il paraît que sur les planètes, l'obscurité et la lumière s'enchaînent... Qu'est-ce qu'il faut pas entendre ! »

languages.text: "Bütün ömrüm Binliman'da geçti. Gezegenlerde hava bir karanlık bir aydınlık oluyormuş. Resmen zırvalık!"

traits.locale_text: "Benim bütün ömrüm Binliman’da geçti. Güya dünyalar bazen karanlık, bazen aydınlık oluyormuş... Zırvaya bak!"
